Simple Idea

How strong a network is if nodes fail.

Mental Model

If one friend leaves group:

does group break?

Strong network → still connected
Weak network → breaks

Why It Matters

Used in:

internet design

social platforms

security

Memory Trick

Robust = Strong network

6️⃣ Homophily
